<br>
As for the PH genoids... ummm well, I tried quading them but my quad &quot;poofed&quot; after falling through the world. I pulled a second quad, same thing. By the third quad I figured out exactly where they were falling through... and they fell through. Now I'm NOT saying exploit something like this... but you can poof them faster than you can kill them, and without the faction  hits <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
BTW I left with 5 of each gem type that evening.<br>
