I spent all of level's 58 and 59 at geo's and also got my shawl gems there. It takes some practice but you can easily quad them without having them dissappear or poof or fall through the world.<br>
<br>
I single pull the shamans as they mess up quads. Also, if a Shaman spawns in one of the spots thats close enough for them to SoW the other geo's......pull those others with snare.<br>
<br>
Just avoid running them in to walls for the most part and you'll be fine. The first big rock closest to where the first 3 geo's spawn is where they poof. Not at the rock, but around that circle area where one spawns on the left. I don't recommend doing this unless you're about to die. It IS an exploit. <br>
<br>
